287
00:12:15,882 --> 00:12:19,282
Those are the bruises of
someone that runs away.

288
00:12:19,315 --> 00:12:21,915
Bruises don't affect men.

289
00:12:21,948 --> 00:12:24,882
They ignore their injuries when
they confront things head on.

290
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:31,682
