-So, give me one good reason
why I should participate.

295
00:13:09,839 --> 00:13:12,606
IKKAKU: Sorry,
Captain Hitsugaya.

296
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:14,372
Please accept this.

297
00:13:14,406 --> 00:13:16,372
-Don't try to bribe
me with sweets.

298
00:13:16,406 --> 00:13:19,406
-So, you say that,
but you're already

