-I'm very sorry, Captain.

303
00:13:30,406 --> 00:13:32,139
But this is a
token of my regret.

304
00:13:34,839 --> 00:13:36,372
-You bastard.

305
00:13:36,406 --> 00:13:38,272
-I'm glad my younger
brother in grade school

306
00:13:38,306 --> 00:13:41,039
