310
00:13:51,006 --> 00:13:54,172
-I want to win this match,
and I want to win it bad.

311
00:13:54,206 --> 00:13:56,572
-I warned you that
it was a bad idea

312
00:13:56,606 --> 00:13:59,239
to get yourself involved
in the lives of humans.

313
00:13:59,272 --> 00:13:59,806
-Sorry.

314
00:13:59,839 --> 00:14:00,872
You're right.

315
00:14:00,906 --> 00:14:02,606
-Yeah, you should be sorry.

316
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:04,239
We're busy here with
training, and it's

317
00:14:04,272 --> 00:14:05,806
a real inconvenience for us.

318
00:14:05,839 --> 00:14:07,039
-Inconvenience?

319
00:14:07,072 --> 00:14:08,472
Then tell me why you're here.

320
00:14:08,506 --> 00:14:10,739
-Well, uh--
actually, Kisuke kept

321
