322
00:14:19,639 --> 00:14:20,806
-Ah, Renji.

323
00:14:20,839 --> 00:14:22,006
And Chad.

324
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:24,339
We're going to wrap up all
the training for today,

325
00:14:24,372 --> 00:14:26,072
