336
00:14:42,606 --> 00:14:44,872
-It's a shame I'm
taking your time up.

337
00:14:44,906 --> 00:14:47,306
-Did you give Kisuke a box of
sweets just so he'd do this?

338
00:14:47,339 --> 00:14:48,972
