404
00:17:23,372 --> 00:17:23,839
-Yah!

405
00:17:31,239 --> 00:17:33,239
-Ikkaku, don't be late.

406
00:17:33,272 --> 00:17:35,406
-I'm going to have to
leave for a moment.

407
00:17:35,439 --> 00:17:36,806
-Huh?

408
00:17:36,839 --> 00:17:38,206
-We will win.

409
00:17:38,239 --> 00:17:42,272
You see, my opponent will be
defeated, so we can't lose.

410
00:17:42,306 --> 00:17:45,372
You're the one who
wants it most, so fight,

411
00:17:45,406 --> 00:17:47,606
and become a real man.

412
00:17:47,639 --> 00:17:48,106
-Ah?

413
00:17:48,139 --> 00:17:48,972
