415
00:17:50,472 --> 00:17:51,706
Transforming?

416
00:17:51,739 --> 00:17:53,572
I wonder where he went?

417
00:17:53,606 --> 00:17:55,872
Huh?

418
00:17:55,906 --> 00:17:57,606
-I'm scared.

419
00:17:57,639 --> 00:17:59,306
-I'm going to lay here
on the ground 'til

420
00:17:59,339 --> 00:18:00,906
my master gets back.

421
00:18:00,939 --> 00:18:01,772
"Nyar."

422
00:18:01,806 --> 00:18:02,872
-Huh?

423
00:18:02,906 --> 00:18:05,772
-If you even look at me,
