00:18:08,572 --> 00:18:11,406
-There's so many men here.

427
00:18:11,439 --> 00:18:13,272
-Have their personalities
all been altered?

428
00:18:13,306 --> 00:18:15,639
ANNOUNCER: Round four
participants, come forward!

429
00:18:15,672 --> 00:18:16,139
-Yes.

430
00:18:19,939 --> 00:18:22,372
