431
00:18:22,406 --> 00:18:26,939
-(THINKING) Indeed, even if I
lose, Ikkaku will avenge us.

432
00:18:26,972 --> 00:18:29,772
But, I have to try.

433
00:18:29,806 --> 00:18:30,272
-Begin.

434
00:18:36,639 --> 00:18:38,572
-Zabimaru!

435
00:18:38,606 --> 00:18:41,506
