some divine retribution!

446
00:19:22,006 --> 00:19:24,472
KEIGO: But even if he
loses, Ikkaku will win!

447
00:19:24,506 --> 00:19:25,739
MIZUHO: Shut up!

448
00:19:25,772 --> 00:19:26,939
