to this unless I win.

450
00:19:32,306 --> 00:19:34,739
-Shinji, try to be more careful.

451
00:19:34,772 --> 00:19:35,906
-Don't push it so hard.

452
00:19:35,939 --> 00:19:36,972
-(THINKING) Upperclassmen?

453
00:19:39,839 --> 00:19:41,439
