454
00:19:41,472 --> 00:19:46,672
I'm going to beat this
guy and become a real man.

455
00:19:46,706 --> 00:19:48,739
-You really are annoying.

456
00:19:48,772 --> 00:19:51,039
-You wait for me, Shinji.

457
00:19:51,072 --> 00:19:53,739
